                    <span>It is hard to accept the basic conclusions of the author, especially if one has faith in the Shroud of Turin. Yet the universe created in this work opens many doors. It may be the best read in the category of hidden knowlege to come along.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Fascinating if not slightly hard to read</div>
